description:
Bobo has a new weapon of choice.

Khalyla is threatened by this weapon of choice. 

Gilbo is accused of inappropriate gift giving.

We talk Brooke Shields, the magic of turns, and long walks in the wild.

 

Recorded June 1, 2016

Music by Bobby Lee
